丽贝卡·阿德勒是一位幼儿园教师，这天上课后没多久，她开始出现[[失语症|言语困难]]并且倒在地下后开始抽搐。[[詹姆士·威尔森_(豪斯医生)|詹姆士·威尔森]]医生（[[罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德|罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德]]饰）试图说服对[[人类|人类]]充满厌恶情绪的格里高利·豪斯医生对阿德勒展开治疗，但豪斯觉得这个病例肯定会很无聊，所以无视了威尔森的要求，后者于是声称病人是自己的表妹，豪斯终于同意接手。院长[[丽莎·卡蒂|丽莎·卡蒂]]（{{lang|en|Lisa Cuddy}}，[[莉萨·埃德尔斯坦|莉萨·埃德尔斯坦]]饰）在[[电梯|电梯]]里要求豪斯充分履行带领医院预约诊疗部门的职责，豪斯因为接到的病例中大多都很简单，没有挑战性而感到厌恶，他拒绝了院长的要求，声称自己拥有任期保障，卡蒂不能解雇他，然后就匆忙离开了。豪斯手下的医生准备对阿德勒进行[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]检查，但却发现豪斯的诊断许可已经遭到撤销，不过卡蒂接下来恢复了许可，条件是豪斯要在诊疗部门好好工作。

正当大家重新开始[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]检查时，阿德勒的喉头出现堵塞而无法[[呼吸|呼吸]]，豪斯手下的[[罗伯特·蔡斯|罗伯特·蔡斯]]（{{lang|en|Robert Chase}}，[[杰西·斯宾塞|杰西·斯宾塞]]饰）和[[阿莉森·卡梅伦|阿莉森·卡梅伦]]（{{lang|en|Allison Cameron}}，[[詹妮弗·莫里森|詹妮弗·莫里森]]饰）不得不实施[[气管切开术|气管切开术]]才令病人幸免于难。另一边的豪斯则在给一个十岁大的男孩看病，他的[[母亲|母亲]]没有按照医嘱的那样每天给孩子使用[[哮喘|哮喘]][[吸入器|吸入器]]，中间时常有所中断，豪斯于是斥责这位母亲在没有对哮喘有足够了解的情况下擅自作出如此重大的决定。豪斯突然想到了什么，于是马上离开前去对阿德勒展开治疗，他诊断病人患有颅内[[血管炎|血管炎]]，只是没有办法证实。豪斯给阿德勒服用[[类固醇|类固醇]]，她马上有所好转，但好景不长，病人情况又开始急剧恶化，比起之前还要严重。

在豪斯的坚持下，卡梅伦与神经科医师[[埃里克·福尔曼|埃里克·福尔曼]]（{{lang|en|Eric Foreman}}，[[欧玛·艾普斯|欧玛·艾普斯]]饰）一起偷爬进阿德勒家里，寻找任何有可能导致阿德勒出现抽搐、言语困难，以及呼吸道收缩的物品。两人在[[厨房|厨房]]找到一包已经打开，但[[符合教规的食物_(犹太教)|犹太教]]民不能食用的[[火腿|火腿]]，福尔曼因此确定病人肯定不会是威尔森的亲人，因为威尔森是[[犹太人|犹太人]]，在肉食上很讲究，只能食用符合教规的食物。豪斯虽然知道朋友通过蒙骗来令自己诊治这个病人，但他选择不予理会，继续诊断，他认为阿德勒是因为吃了没煮熟的[[猪肉|猪肉]]而患上[[囊虫病|囊虫病]]，她体内的[[绦虫纲|绦虫]]繁殖时，其幼虫经血液流经并感染了[[大脑|大脑]]。阿德勒希望能够体面地去世，因此拒绝接受任何治疗，除非诊断结果得到证据的佐证，豪斯无法拿出这样的证据，于是试图加以说服。阿德勒问起豪斯，他的右腿为什么会一瘸一拐的，豪斯告诉她，自己的大腿肌肉之前因[[梗塞|梗塞]]而坏死，如果当年为他治疗的大夫做出正确的诊断，这样的事情本可以避免。豪斯接下来表示，死亡永远都是丑陋恶心的，任何人，包括阿德勒在内都不可能体面地死去，但她仍然不改初衷。正当豪斯准备放弃时，蔡斯想到了一个既不用动手术，又可以提供绦虫感染证据的办法，医生们给病人的腿照了[[X射线|X光片]]，豪斯通过X光片向阿德勒证明，她的确感染了绦虫，并且这种疾病是完全可以治愈的。看到证据的阿德勒终于同意接受治疗，服下了可以杀死绦虫的药片。几天后，她幼儿园班上的全部16个孩子以及另一位老师都一起来医院探视，阿德勒也向他们伸出了双手。

== 制作 ==
=== 构思和拍摄 ===
[[File:David_Shore_Cropped.jpg|thumb]]
《豪斯医生》的主创人大卫·肖曾在一家教学医院看病，这段经历成为他创作本剧的一个重要原因。回首往事时，肖表示：“我知道，我一出房门，他们就会毫不留情地嘲笑我（的无知），而我觉得，要是让一个（医生）角色在病人还没离开房间时就这样做，效果应该会很有意思。”<ref name="hulu-developing the concept">{{cite web | author = Shore, David | year = 2006 | url = http://www.hulu.com/watch/21606/house-house---developing-the-concept#s-p2-st-i1 | title = Developing The Concept | work = Hulu.com | publisher = The Paley Center for Media | accessdate = 2009-03-24 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090324225402/http://www.hulu.com/watch/21606/house-house---developing-the-concept#s-p2-st-i1 | archivedate = 2009-03-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。2004年，肖与两位[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]凯蒂·雅各布斯（{{lang|en|Katie Jacobs}}）和保罗·阿坦纳西奥（{{lang|en|Paul Attanasio}}）一起向福克斯提议了医疗侦探剧《豪斯医生》，医院中的大夫将会像侦探一样寻找病因，至于豪斯一角的构思则是在福克斯买下这个节目之后增加的<ref name="u of t">{{cite web | author = Gibson, Stacy | date = 2008 Winter | archivedate = 2012-11-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121126125721/http://www.magazine.utoronto.ca/cover-story/david-shore-house-creator-television-producers/ | url = http://www.magazine.utoronto.ca/cover-story/david-shore-house-creator-television-producers/ | title = The House that Dave Built | publisher = University of Toronto Magazine | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。肖根据自己预约一位医生就诊的经历编写了试播集的剧本<ref name="EW1" />，他曾因髋关节疼痛前去就医，但与医生的预约却需要等上两个礼拜，到了这个时候，自己的髋部已经不痛了。不过肖表示当时这位医生还是“客气到有些不可思议”，他之后还表示，自己在撰写试播集剧本的过程中爱上了这个角色，喜欢上了这样一个会真的向病人说出“我干嘛要浪费你的时间呢？”这种话的医生<ref name="EW1">{{cite news |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,1043940,00.html |title=Dr. Feelbad |publisher=''Entertainment Weekly'' |date=2005-04-08 |author=Jensen, Jeff |accessdate=2014-03-20 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211092240/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C1043940%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-12-11 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

《豪斯医生》的一个核心前提就是主角在行动上有所不便。剧组起初的构思是豪斯需要坐轮椅<ref>{{cite news | author = Carter, Bill | date = 2007-01-30 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2007/01/30/arts/television/30hous.html/?_r=2& | title =‘House,’ Already Strong, Gets a Boost | work = The New York Times | accessdate = 2014-03-20}}</ref>，但福克斯拒绝了这一思路，于是剧组又在主角的脸上加上一道疤痕，最后再定为让豪斯因腿脚不便而需要使用拐杖，主创人员之后表示，他们很感激福克斯没有让豪斯坐上轮椅<ref name="int-disability">{{cite web | author = Shore, David; Jacobs, Katie | year = 2006 | archivedate = 2013-06-17 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130617033642/http://www.hulu.com/watch/21680#s-p2-st-i1 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.hulu.com/watch/21680#s-p2-st-i1 | title = House's Disability | work = Hulu.com | publisher = The Paley Center for Media | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。主角在起初的剧本中是34岁年纪，但肖之后表示他希望让这个角色更老一些<ref name="BTVLaurie">{{cite news | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/how-hugh-laurie-got-into-house-20722.aspx | title = How Hugh Laurie Got into 'House' | publisher = BuddyTV | date = 2008-06-24 | author = DeLeon, Kris | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121019154810/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/how-hugh-laurie-got-into-house-20722.aspx | archivedate = 2012-10-19 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。

试播集由大卫·肖编剧<ref name="torontosun-laurie" />，拍摄工作则在[[加拿大|加拿大]]举行，之后的剧集则大部分都是在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]]的摄影棚摄制<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | date = 2006-01-29 | url = http://www.etonline.com/tv/2006/01/35979/index.html | title = Behind the Scenes of 'House' | publisher = Entertainment Tonight | accessdate = 2008-09-17 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2008-07-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080710072927/http://www.etonline.com/tv/2006/01/35979/index.html }}</ref>。肖还表示，《[[纽约客|纽约客]]》在职作家[[伯顿·罗切|伯顿·罗切]]（{{lang|en|Berton Roueché}}）笔下的许多耐人寻味的医疗案例对试播集和早期的多集节目剧情提供了灵感<ref name="u of t" />。

=== 演员选择 ===
制片人布莱恩·辛格起初要求豪斯一角一定要由一位美国演员来演，他表示自己看到很多外国演员前来试镜后，心里越来越觉得非美国人不可。休·劳瑞于本剧选角期间正在参加电影《[[凤凰劫_(2004年电影)|凤凰劫]]》（{{lang|en|''Flight of the Phoenix''}}）的拍摄，他在[[纳米比亚|纳米比亚]]一间酒店的浴室拍了一卷试镜录像带，这是他在当地唯一能找到充足光线的地方<ref>{{cite news | author = Keveney, Bill | date = 2004-11-16 | title = Hugh Laurie gets into 'House' | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131222024905/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2004-11-15-hugh-laurie_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/news/2004-11-15-hugh-laurie_x.htm | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | archivedate = 2013-12-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，他在视频中对自己的形象和镜头里的环境致歉，辛格则觉得这段视频看上去和“[[奥萨马·本·拉登|本·拉登]]的视频”有得一比<ref name="torontosun-laurie" />。劳瑞现场即兴发挥，用一把[[雨伞|雨伞]]充当拐杖<ref name="BTVLaurie" />。辛格对男演员的表现留下了深刻印象，之后还称赞这位“美国演员”是如何准确地把握了人物特点，完全没想到劳瑞其实是英国人<ref name="hulu-developing the concept" />。

劳瑞起初以为豪斯只不过是威尔森一角的“陪衬”，因为根据剧本中的描写，威尔森是一位长相“天真”的医生，他一直到念完整本剧本后才意识到原来自己获演的是主角<ref name="Inside">{{cite episode | title = Hugh Laurie Interview | episodelink = | series = Inside the Actor's Studio | serieslink = | credits = | network = BRAVO Network | station = | airdate = 2006 | season = 12 | seriesno = | number = 189 | minutes = }}</ref>。据肖表示：“要让人讨厌一个混蛋那太容易了，真正困难的是要让节目有看头。休带来了我们所需要的一切，那种龌龊，那种[[政治正确|政治上不正确]]的东西。但是你还是想要看到他，想要花时间和他在一起。”<ref name="torontosun-laurie">{{cite news | author = Brioux, Bill | date = 2004-11-14 | title = Compelling 'House' Doctor | work = The Toronto Sun | page = TV2}}</ref>

试播集中的豪斯与知名虚构侦探[[夏洛克·福尔摩斯|夏洛克·福尔摩斯]]存在多个相似之处，肖对此表示，他一直是福尔摩斯的粉丝，并且发现这个角色存在一个独特之处，那就是对他的客户比较冷淡<ref name="hulu-developing the concept" />。豪斯和福尔摩斯都只有一个真正的朋友（分别是威尔森和华生），这个朋友也是主人翁与人际社会之间的联系所在。制片人希望在豪斯和威尔森之间也建立着这种福尔摩斯和华生间的动态关系，特别是角色间的化学反应方面<ref>{{cite news | author=Werts, Diane | title = 'House' thrives with inspiration from Sherlock Holmes | work = The Philadelphia Inquirer | date = 2006-09-04}}</ref>。

扮演詹姆士·威尔森医生的罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德当时已经看过《[[数字追凶|数字追凶]]》的试播集剧本，正准备参加试镜，但之后还是前来参加了《豪斯医生》的试镜，因为他很希望能出演一个主角所依靠人物，也很喜欢这个故事和夏洛克·福尔摩斯的相似之处<ref>{{cite web | author = Leonard, Robert | year = 2006 | archivedate = 2012-10-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121016215007/http://www.hulu.com/watch/21682#s-p1-st-i1 | url = http://www.hulu.com/watch/21682#s-p1-st-i1 | title = Robert Sean Leonard On His Audition | work = Hulu.com | publisher = The Paley Center for Media | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。莱纳德觉得自己试镜时表现欠差，不过由于他和辛格是老朋友，所以最后还是得到了这个角色<ref>{{cite web |author=Wolk, Josh |date=2007-07-03 |archivedate=2013-12-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131211073123/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C20044586%2C00.html |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20044586,00.html |title=A Summer Away from the 'House' |work=Entertainment Weekly |accessdate=2014-03-20 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。接受采访时，莱纳德这样回答有关他的角色为什么能够和豪斯成为朋友的问题：

{{quote|我觉得，威尔森会容忍豪斯，和每星期里有数百万人们愿意收看这个节目的原因是一样的。我认为他真的充满了活力，也很风趣，胆大妄为而且还会自嘲。我认为这都是一些吸引人的特质，并且他说话很直截了当。在钱方面来说，他没打算还你钱，但我有老多朋友都是这样，所以我也就并不觉得这里面有多么不可思议。我觉得豪斯是个非常吸引人的角色，相信大多数人都会想和他交朋友。|罗伯特·肖恩·莱纳德|接受{{lang|en|[[BuddyTV|BuddyTV]]}}的采访<ref>{{cite web | author = Kubicek, John | date = 2007-10-09 | archivedate = 2012-01-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120105094153/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/exclusive-interview-house-star-12201.aspx | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/exclusive-interview-house-star-12201.aspx | title = Exclusive Interview: 'House' Star Robert Sean Leonard | publisher = BuddyTV | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>}}

[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]男演员[[杰西·斯宾塞|杰西·斯宾塞]]的经济人建议他参加蔡斯一角试镜，但他对此有些拿不定主意，担心节目和《[[综合医院|综合医院]]》（{{lang|en|''General Hospital''}}）这样的[[肥皂剧|肥皂剧]]雷同。但他看到剧本后就改变了主意<ref>{{cite news |author=Staff |date=2007-09-17 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-02-24 |work=The Star |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224235743/http://ecentral.my/news/story.asp?file=%2F2007%2F9%2F17%2Ftvnradio%2F18869314&sec=tvnradio |url=http://www.star-ecentral.com/news/story.asp?file=/2007/9/17/tvnradio/18869314&sec=tvnradio |title=Doctor in the house |accessdate=2012-02-24 }}</ref>，并开始努力说服制片人把这个角色改写成澳大利亚人<ref>{{cite news |author=Marquand, Sarrah |date=2006-10-04 |url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,20517580-5003422,00.html |title=Young doctor |work=The Courier-Mail |accessdate=2008-09-27 |archivedate=2010-02-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100201051537/http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0%2C23739%2C20517580-5003422%2C00.html }}</ref>。诠释埃里克·福尔曼一角的欧玛·艾普斯（{{lang|en|Omar Epps}}）之前曾在医务剧《[[急诊室的故事|急诊室的故事]]》里出演一位陷入困境的实习医生，这段经历对他在本剧的演出产生了影响<ref>{{cite web | author =  | date = 2007-10-11 | url = http://television.aol.com/tv-celebrity-interviews/omar-epps | title = Omar Epps Is Back in the 'House'! | publisher = AOL-Time Warner | accessdate = 2008-09-28 | archivedate = 2007-08-19 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070819092237/http://television.aol.com/tv-celebrity-interviews/omar-epps }}</ref>。艾普斯和另一位演员[[詹妮弗·莫里森|詹妮弗·莫里森]]在看过剧本后都认为，这个节目要么会大获成功，要么就默默无闻<ref>{{cite web | author = Dahl, Oscar | date = 2007-10-16 | url = http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/exclusive-interview-omar-epps-12502.aspx | title = Exclusive Interview: Omar Epps and Jennifer Morrison, from 'House' | publisher = BuddyTV | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130907072623/http://www.buddytv.com/articles/house/exclusive-interview-omar-epps-12502.aspx | archivedate = 2013-09-07 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2014-03-20 }}</ref>。

== 反响 ==
《豪斯医生》的试播集获得了总体较为正面的评价。评论家对豪斯一角给予好评<ref name="dailytelegraph-postrev">{{cite news | author = Davies, Hugh | date = 2004-11-20 | title = Dr Laurie has viewers of US TV in stitches | work = The Daily Telegraph | page = N9 | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | archivedate = 2014-01-10 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140110004618/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1477057/Dr-Laurie-has-viewers-of-US-TV-in-stitches.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/1477057/Dr-Laurie-has-viewers-of-US-TV-in-stitches.html }}</ref><ref name="usatoday-review">{{cite news | author = Bianco, Robert | date = 2004-11-14 | archivedate = 2012-10-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121022104545/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2004-11-15-house_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/life/television/reviews/2004-11-15-house_x.htm | title = There's a doctor worth watching in 'House' | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | page = D1 }}</ref>。《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的[[汤姆·谢尔斯|汤姆·谢尔斯]]（{{lang|en|Tom Shales}}）称其为“多年来电视上最激动人心的角色”<ref name="washingtonpost-review">{{cite news | author = Shales, Tom | date = 2004-11-16 | title = 'House': Watching Is the Best Medicine | work = The Washington Post | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A53025-2004Nov15.html | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | quote = the most electrifying character to hit television in years. | archive-date = 2018-08-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180809112434/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/articles/A53025-2004Nov15.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《纽约杂志》（{{lang|en|''The New York Magazine''}}）称赞这是最让人满意的医疗电视剧集，抓住了其中最基本的精髓，文章中还盛赞了演员的表现，认为剧中的职业演员表现出了医生对病人的真正关怀<ref>{{cite news | last = Leonard | first = John | title = Scrub Par | page = 1 | publisher = New York Magazine | date = 2004-11-15 | archivedate = 2013-12-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212163652/http://nymag.com/nymetro/arts/tv/reviews/10331/ | url = http://nymag.com/nymetro/arts/tv/reviews/10331/ | accessdate = 2014-03-20 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。而《[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Boston Globe''}}）的马修·吉尔伯特（{{lang|en|Matthew Gilbert}}）则称赞本集没有通过粉饰人物的缺陷来减轻观众对“[[健康维护组织|健康维护组织]]工厂”的恐惧<ref>{{cite news | author = Gilbert, Matt | date = 2004-11-16 | title = Strong Prognosis for medical show | work = The Boston Globe | page = D1 | quote = What a treat it is to find a medical show that doesn't turn its talented MDs into bedside saints in order to calm viewers' fears about mechanical HMO factories. | archivedate = 2006-12-01 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20061201192004/http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2004/11/16/strong_prognosis_for_medical_show_house_laurie_fascinates_as_doctor_in_house/ | url = http://www.boston.com/ae/tv/articles/2004/11/16/strong_prognosis_for_medical_show_house_laurie_fascinates_as_doctor_in_house/ }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的亚历山德拉·斯坦利（{{lang|en|Alessandra Stanley}}）表示，虽然剧中人物可能会让部分观众感到扫兴，但节目的血腥和相应衍生的枝节对于医疗剧迷来说有着正面的影响<ref name="nyt-review" />。《[[电视指南_(杂志)|电视指南]]》的马特·劳什（{{lang|en|Matt Roush}}）认为，《豪斯医生》是“典型医务剧的一次非典型治疗”<ref>{{cite news | title = Roush Review, Doctor Feel bad; Don't ask this grouch to make house calls | author = Roush, Matt | date = 2004-11-08 | publisher = ''TV Guide'' | page = 1 | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140321014122/http://www.tvguide.com/roush/doctor-feelbad-dont-26867.aspx | url = http://www.tvguide.com/roush/doctor-feelbad-dont-26867.aspx }}</ref>。《[[影音俱乐部|影音俱乐部]]》则称《豪斯医生》是福克斯继1996年的电视短剧《[[利益_(电视剧)|利益]]》（{{lang|en|''Profit''}}）以来“最肮脏”的[[黑色幽默|黑色喜剧]]<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.avclub.com/content/node/24686 | title = A Guide for the Compulsive TV Fan | author = Gillette, Amelie; Murray, Noel & Phipps, Keith | date = 2004-11-22 | publisher = The A.V. Club | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080921222504/http://www.avclub.com/content/node/24686 | archivedate = 2008-09-21 | accessdate = 2008-11-23 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。多位剧评人认为，这部电视剧是福克斯所有定期播放[[真人实境秀|真人实境剧]]中的一大亮点<ref name="nyt-review">{{cite news | author = Stanley, Alessandra | date = 2004-11-16 | title = With Terminal Witticism, Even Cancer Can Be Fun | work = The New York Times | page = E5 | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/16/arts/television/16stan.html?_r=0 | archivedate = 2013-05-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130520155046/http://www.nytimes.com/2004/11/16/arts/television/16stan.html }}</ref><ref name="variety-prev">{{cite news | author = Lowry, Brian | date = 2004-11-21 | title = Fox prescribes edgy Rx for a dramatic improvement | url = http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/15087819/fox-prescribes-edgy-rx-dramatic-improvement | work = Variety | page = 57 | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archive-date = 2014-03-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140321043349/http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/15087819/fox-prescribes-edgy-rx-dramatic-improvement | dead-url = no }}</ref>。而负面评价方面则主要是针对配角都是些年轻、英俊、漂亮的医生，存在其它医务剧中的俗套<ref name="new yorker">{{cite news | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111210551/http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2004/11/29/041129crte_television | url = http://www.newyorker.com/archive/2004/11/29/041129crte_television | author = Franklin, Nancy | date = 2004-11-29 | title = Playing Doctor | work = The New Yorker | page = 168 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="dailynews-review">{{cite news | author = Bianculli, David | date = 2004-11-16 | title = 'House' gets fine treatment | work = Daily News | page = 107}}</ref>。

一些媒体将本集的节目形式与同期播出的另一部医务剧《[[医雾调查|医雾调查]]》（{{lang|en|''Medical Investigation''}}）相比较。《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》认为《豪斯医生》中以人物推动的结构形式要优于《医雾调查》中以情节驱动的形式<ref name="usatoday-review" />，《[[旧金山纪事报|旧金山纪事报]]》则认为《豪斯医生》由于主角塑造的成功而比《医雾调查》更加优秀<ref name="sfgate-review">{{cite news | author = Goodman, Tim | date = 2004-11-15 | archivedate = 2013-10-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131001211755/http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Network-meddling-by-Fox-execs-starts-the-2635158.php | deadurl = no | work = San Francisco Chronicle | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | url = http://www.sfgate.com/entertainment/article/Network-meddling-by-Fox-execs-starts-the-2635158.php | title = Network meddling by Fox execs starts the deathwatch for 'House' }}</ref>。不过，《[[综艺|综艺]]》的布莱恩·洛瑞（{{lang|en|Brian Lowry}}）认为两部医疗剧过于类似，并且《豪斯医生》没有达到福克斯电视台其他节目的水准<ref name="new yorker" /><ref name="variety-prev" />。《{{lang|en|[[Slate|Slate]]}}》杂志的[[谢尔温·努兰|谢尔温·努兰]]（{{lang|en|Sherwin Nuland}}）对试播集的评价非常负面，他认为剧中错漏连篇，并且最重要的是主角性格上如此粗枝大叶，对病人如此疏远，这样的医生在任何一家医院都将无法立足<ref name="slate-review">{{cite news | url = http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2004/11/is_there_a_doctor_in_the_house.html | author = Nuland, Sherwin | date = 2004-11-30 | title = Is There a Doctor in the House? | work = Slate | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140225022658/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2004/11/is_there_a_doctor_in_the_house.html | archivedate = 2014-02-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。《[[西雅图时报|西雅图时报]]》的凯·麦克法登（{{lang|en|Kay McFadden}}）觉得劳瑞的刻画让豪斯一角更为人性化，但他也在评论中指出，节目最大的漏洞在于其情节上的趣味性留于表面，没有朝医务剧可以朝向的深层次发展<ref>{{cite news | author = McFadden, Kay | date = 2004-11-15 | url = http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20041115&slug=kay15 | title = It's worth making a "House" call tomorrow | work = The Seattle Times | accessdate = 2014-03-21 | archivedate = 2014-02-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140223094615/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20041115&slug=kay15 }}</ref>。还有评论中批评了节目中的配角在最初的几集中都没有表现出性格特点<ref name="autogenerated1">{{cite web | author = McFarland, Melanie | date = 2004-11-16 | archivedate = 2014-02-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140224052438/http://www.seattlepi.com/ae/tv/article/Fox-s-medical-drama-House-is-a-welcome-1159563.php | url = http://www.seattlepi.com/ae/tv/article/Fox-s-medical-drama-House-is-a-welcome-1159563.php | title = Fox's medical drama 'House' is a welcome transfusion of quality programming | work = Seattle Post-Intelligencer | accessdate = 2014-03-21 }}</ref>。

试播集在美国首播时吸引了约700万观众收看，这个成绩可以在2004年11月15至21日这个星期的所有[[电视节目|电视节目]]中排到第62位<ref name="viewer" />。节目于2005年6月9日通过第五台在英国首播，获得了10%的收视率（180万观众）<ref>{{cite news | author = Brook, Stephen | date = 2005-06-10 | archivedate = 2012-11-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121113223129/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2005/jun/10/overnights | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2005/jun/10/overnights | title = Springwatch gives BBC2 a natural high | work = The Guardian | accessdate = 2014-03-21 }}</ref>。为试播集以及整个[[豪斯医生_(第1季)|第一季]]谱曲的克里斯托弗·霍格（{{lang|en|Christopher Hoag}}）因本集的音乐获得了第57届[[黄金时段艾美奖|黄金时段艾美奖]]的杰出配乐奖提名<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.emmys.org/awards/2005pt/awards/music.php | title = 57th annual Emmy awards | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | date = 2005-09-18 | accessdate = 2008-08-27 | archivedate = 2007-09-27 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927002001/http://www.emmys.org/awards/2005pt/awards/music.php }}</ref>。大卫·肖因本集的编剧工作获得了一项[[人道奖|人道奖]]提名，但最终获奖的是为《[[白宫群英|白宫群英]]》编剧的[[约翰·威尔斯|约翰·威尔斯]]（{{lang|en|John Wells}}）<ref name="Humanitas05">{{cite news |archivedate=2014-03-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140321032245/http://humanitasprize.info/HUMANITAS-NEWS-2000s/2005%20June%20-%20%27HOTEL%20RWANDA%27%20named%20among%202005%20HUMANITAS%20finalists.pdf |url=http://humanitasprize.info/HUMANITAS-NEWS-2000s/2005%20June%20-%20'HOTEL%20RWANDA'%20named%20among%202005%20HUMANITAS%20finalists.pdf |title='Hotel Rwanda' named among 2005 Humanitas finalists |author=Doyle, Paula |work=humanitasprize.info |date=2005-06-24 |accessdate=2014-03-21 |format=PDF }}</ref><ref name="Huminwon">{{cite web | url = http://www.humanitasprize.org/winners60m.htm | title = Winners of the Humanitas Prize 60 Minute Category | accessdate = 2009-11-19 | publisher = Humanitas Prize | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2009-11-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091119102650/http://www.humanitasprize.org/winners60m.htm }}</ref>。

